    "en": {
      "name": "Goblin Biker Grand Crisis",
      "effect": "You can target 1 \"Goblin\" monster you control and 1 monster your opponent controls, OR 1 \"Goblin\" monster in your GY and 1 monster in your opponent's GY; banish both. You can send this face-up card from your Spell & Trap Zone to the GY, then target 5 of your banished \"Goblin\" monsters with different names; Special Summon them. You can only use 1 \"Goblin Biker Grand Crisis\" effect per turn, and only once that turn.",
      "official": false
    },
